<br>
Hiero Cloak is not an upgrade over SBC for a monk.  You get 1 more AC and 5 more hps.  You get agi which though crappy will probably make up that 1 AC, and the SBC only weighs 0.1, where the hiero cloak weighs 1.0<br>
<br>
For me, the SBC would be a slight upgrade as it would allow me to use another Tink Bag.<br>
<br>
They really are very close though.  If you are hitting 205 stamina then go with the hiero cloak but that's the only situation I could see it being an upgrade in.  Otherwise it's a +5hp -5str -5dex +.9wgt switch from SBC to Hiero. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=46329"><img src="http://www.netwalk.com/~loki/signaturevara.jpg"><BR>60 Iksar Grandmaster<a> - Shackle of Tynnonium - Celestial Fist -<BR>
